                /** @description Per-session ('this conversation only') DISABLED tool names — a JSON-encoded array (e.g. ['exec','agent']). The use case drops these from the per-turn advertised tool schemas. Applied per-turn only; never mutates the global tool-safety config. Omitted/empty ⇒ the full default tool set. Additive query param (refactor-plan §3.1). */
